post.description:
Duplicate assets based on the selection context to the given destination folder.
 For duplicating the hierarchy of folders, use the depth parameter. Using selection context to expand will flatten out the asset structure and duplicate it.
 Using selection context parameter to duplicate hierarchy of asset will result in validation error.<p>While using selection context to filter the assets based on permissions, pass permissions_filter paramater in selection context. The valid permission filters are {ASSETVIEW_PERM, SUMMARYVIEW_PERM, PREVIEWVIEW_PERM, EXPORT_PERM, SUBSCRIBE_PERM,METAEDIT_PERM, CONTENTEDIT_PERM, MEMBERSHIPEDIT_PERM, DELETEASSET_PERM, EDITPARENTS_PERM, CUSTOM01_PERM, CUSTOM02_PERM, CUSTOM03_PERM, CUSTOM04_PERM}
